---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Terms of Service | Novelty Ads" description="Novelty Ads Terms of Service." canonical="https://noveltyads.com/terms-of-service/" noindex={true}>
<section class="page-hero" style="padding:100px 0 60px;">
  <div class="container" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <h1 class="page-hero__title" data-reveal="up">Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="page-hero__sub" data-reveal="up">Last updated: January 2025</p>
  </div>
</section>
<section style="padding:60px 0 120px;background:#F8F7F4;">
  <div class="container">
    <div style="max-width:740px;margin:0 auto;font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;color:#444;" data-reveal="up">
      <p style="margin-bottom:20px;">By accessing and using noveltyads.com, you accept and agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. Please read them carefully before using our services.</p>
      <h2 style="font-size:22px;font-weight:700;margin:36px 0 12px;color:#0A0A0A;">1. Services</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom:20px;">Novelty Ads provides digital marketing services including web design, SEO, paid advertising, email marketing, Shopify development, and Kickstarter marketing. All services are subject to a separate Service Agreement or Statement of Work.</p>
      <h2 style="font-size:22px;font-weight:700;margin:36px 0 12px;color:#0A0A0A;">2. Payment Terms</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom:20px;">All fees are due as outlined in your individual service agreement. Late payments may result in service suspension. We reserve the right to update pricing with 30 days' notice.</p>
      <h2 style="font-size:22px;font-weight:700;margin:36px 0 12px;color:#0A0A0A;">3. Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom:20px;">Upon full payment, clients own all deliverables created specifically for them. Novelty Ads retains the right to display work in its portfolio unless otherwise agreed in writing.</p>
      <h2 style="font-size:22px;font-weight:700;margin:36px 0 12px;color:#0A0A0A;">4. Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom:20px;">Novelty Ads shall not be liable for indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from the use of our services. Our maximum liability is limited to fees paid in the preceding 3 months.</p>
      <h2 style="font-size:22px;font-weight:700;margin:36px 0 12px;color:#0A0A0A;">5. Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions about these terms? <a href="/contact" style="color:#3A5BF0;font-weight:600;">Contact us</a> and we'll respond within 2 business days.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
